n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"咁要幾多時間計劃好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"起碼都比文宣做下野先啦<br />\n文宣圖又無 有邊個知道你有依個行動姐<br />\n你見其他行動都要出日程表啦 <br />\n無啦啦插隊插個光復上水做乜尻？<br />\n如果係小隊快閃既 就直頭連依個post都可以慳返<br />\n<br />\n但好老實講 北區唔岩大搞 <br />\n我明搞既用意係光復上水 清水貨客 <br />\n我都忍撚左班水貨客好撚耐 日日塞尻住條路<br />\n但你確保手足會忍手？<br />\n<br />\n北區只適合打小隊快閃游擊<br />\n平時只要雞嶺迴旋處塞車 已經導致全上水交通癱瘓 封城咁制<br />\n搞大行動 無地面交通 無黨鐵 北區就會同其他區與世隔絕<br />\n連手足既支援都入唔到啊大佬 <br />\n但POPO就源源不絕有PTUHQ支援<br />\n<br />\n7.13果次真係算好彩嫁咋"},{"pid":"37e856cdc3c2c946daab5cb92a9bf939d06c107e","tid":1672204,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4ce3e52ca811264f3459f2d3f3aecce328ffec38","tid":1672204,"uid":164851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1860a10cb3b9d37f5821cc012fce184b06563b07","tid":1672204,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"37e26c2b1aa41eb08412fb3eb338a494101eab07","tid":1672204,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"拉 又亂搞活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母閪啦<br />\n今日三毛風向係活動唔好搞咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"ust南亞仔都三毛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d966714b45ee96c079a918113b632371c0d885","tid":1672204,"uid":267961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcea293c0513a5ee564718d692dd34293ea68bd2","tid":1672204,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:54:39.000Z","m